{"tid":2318099,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國制裁6船公司一間總部在香港 涉為北韓運煤違制裁令","createTime":"2020-12-09T05:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T06:14:44.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7b5bd85e30ad0a112cd0f547f2b0f23013c9ea","tid":2318099,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/stevenmnuchin1/status/1336386937494581250?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstevenmnuchin1%2Fstatus%2F1336386937494581250%3Fs%3D19&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUJSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=a5863013\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstevenmnuchin1%2Fstatus%2F1336386937494581250%3Fs%3D19&h=d54e3839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/stevenmnuchin1/status/1336386937494581250?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USTreasury/status/1336341942951694337?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSTreasury%2Fstatus%2F1336341942951694337%3Fs%3D19&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUJSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=8e468eba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSTreasury%2Fstatus%2F1336341942951694337%3Fs%3D19&h=f58aa365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USTreasury/status/1336341942951694337?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部周二宣佈制裁六間公司，其中多間總部在中國，另外將四艘船列入黑名單，指之涉嫌非法將北韓煤運出口。<br />\n<br />\n財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）發表聲明，指北韓繼續規避聯合國煤出口禁令，經常利用來自勞改營的強迫勞動採礦，通過剝削人民推展其非法武器計劃。<br />\n<br />\n被制裁的船公司包括總部在中國的WeiHai Huijiang Trade Ltd、Always Smooth Ltd、Good Siblings Ltd。Always Smooth Ltd和Good Siblings Ltd亦有在英國註冊。總部在香港的Silver Bridge Shipping Co-HKG、總部在越南的Thinh Cuong Co Ltd、在北韓和越南運作的Korea Daizin Trading Corporation也在制裁名單上。<br />\n<br />\n列入黑名單的船包括Calm Bridge、Asia Bridge、Lucky Star、Star 18，被指直接從北韓港口將煤裝上船，運送到區內各處。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會2007年禁止北韓出口煤，以截斷平壤大殺傷力武器發展的資金來源。不過，今年初有報告指聯合國一系列針對北韓的制裁措施似乎成效不彰，北韓非法進口越來越多石油，也持續進口豪華汽車和酒精，更繼續透過非法海路出口煤炭和海沙等商品，公然蔑視聯合國安理會的決議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201209/OGIFYZ6OZ5HAJKXOH6CQKZUOK4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201209%2FOGIFYZ6OZ5HAJKXOH6CQKZUOK4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUJSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=2145b635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201209%2FOGIFYZ6OZ5HAJKXOH6CQKZUOK4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=211b5819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201209/OGIFYZ6OZ5HAJKXOH6CQKZUOK4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a>"},{"pid":"222f1ec9eed42512c4251378275433774d1dacc6","tid":2318099,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"支那白手套"},{"pid":"d79cf534693dac1de870eabbe5f766870911b171","tid":2318099,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"岩啦，繼續打"},{"pid":"dd27b98b8d3dbaf6f2fcfb868e4e423fdfb63ef9","tid":2318099,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"拉清單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b72d889c553f38348b22ebb099fd653ec3038f","tid":2318099,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:14:44.000Z","msg":"支那攪人地美國大選 , 美國真係唔會再留手"}]}